{"tid":2350860,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"移民公司料一成BNO港人動身 「移民熱潮已開始」 趕3月底前免稅首置 料移英高峰首季現","createTime":"2021-01-02T16:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-10T11:35:41.000Z","uid":36494,"like":96,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"730946e18f61e7d26ccc28d37ffd96e2e43a8384","tid":2350860,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:28:45.000Z","msg":"BNO簽證今年1月31日開始接受申請，但過去半年已有大批港人以「Leave Outside The Rules」（LOTR）方式率先入境英國。有本港移民顧問形容，隨着BNO簽證推出，「BNO移民熱潮已經開始」，估計或有10%合資格港人會循此計劃移英。他透露過去半年已收到大量有關BNO簽證的查詢，加上英國豁免首置買家在當地置業繳付印花稅的限期會在3月31日屆滿，或促使部分港人趕在限期前於當地置業，預計第一波離港高峰期在首季出現。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210102/s00002/1609525414886/%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e6%96%99%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90bno%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e5%8b%95%e8%ba%ab-%e3%80%8c%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91%e7%86%b1%e6%bd%ae%e5%b7%b2%e9%96%8b%e5%a7%8b%e3%80%8d-%e8%b6%953%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%95%e5%89%8d%e5%85%8d%e7%a8%85%e9%a6%96%e7%bd%ae-%e6%96%99%e7%a7%bb%e8%8b%b1%e9%ab%98%e5%b3%b0%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%8f%be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210102%2Fs00002%2F1609525414886%2F%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%2596%2599%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590bno%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%258b%2595%25e8%25ba%25ab-%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591%25e7%2586%25b1%25e6%25bd%25ae%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e9%2596%258b%25e5%25a7%258b%25e3%2580%258d-%25e8%25b6%25953%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%25ba%2595%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%2585%258d%25e7%25a8%2585%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%25bd%25ae-%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e8%258b%25b1%25e9%25ab%2598%25e5%25b3%25b0%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25ad%25a3%25e7%258f%25be&d=%2Bt7hcjB4BRnTGQ5b2LOb0%2FZtcVXZMMHuQDZeBHkLh3U%3D&h=2f552c1c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20210102%2Fs00002%2F1609525414886%2F%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%258f%25b8%25e6%2596%2599%25e4%25b8%2580%25e6%2588%2590bno%25e6%25b8%25af%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%258b%2595%25e8%25ba%25ab-%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e6%25b0%2591%25e7%2586%25b1%25e6%25bd%25ae%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e9%2596%258b%25e5%25a7%258b%25e3%2580%258d-%25e8%25b6%25953%25e6%259c%2588%25e5%25ba%2595%25e5%2589%258d%25e5%2585%258d%25e7%25a8%2585%25e9%25a6%2596%25e7%25bd%25ae-%25e6%2596%2599%25e7%25a7%25bb%25e8%258b%25b1%25e9%25ab%2598%25e5%25b3%25b0%25e9%25a6%2596%25e5%25ad%25a3%25e7%258f%25be&h=8bef9db8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20210102/s00002/1609525414886/%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91%e5%85%ac%e5%8f%b8%e6%96%99%e4%b8%80%e6%88%90bno%e6%b8%af%e4%ba%ba%e5%8b%95%e8%ba%ab-%e3%80%8c%e7%a7%bb%e6%b0%91%e7%86%b1%e6%bd%ae%e5%b7%b2%e9%96%8b%e5%a7%8b%e3%80%8d-%e8%b6%953%e6%9c%88%e5%ba%95%e5%89%8d%e5%85%8d%e7%a8%85%e9%a6%96%e7%bd%ae-%e6%96%99%e7%a7%bb%e8%8b%b1%e9%ab%98%e5%b3%b0%e9%a6%96%e5%ad%a3%e7%8f%be</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n胡另提到，BNO簽證屬於簡單、容易處理的簽證，只需提供無犯罪紀錄證明書（俗稱「良民證」），以及證明無身體健康問題，故預計稍後接受申請時不會出現特別問題，「相比其他國家，英國本身是較寬鬆的，主要照肺，證明無患上肺結核便可」。不過，他亦提醒港人要留意移英後預計面對的問題，特別是涉及稅項（見另稿）。"},{"pid":"d8a3309d8d1c473e67e8a82ff54428f5719579b3","tid":2350860,"uid":79563,"like":37,"dislike":9,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"LOCKDOWN 緊<br />\n<br />\nQ1 移條毛?"},{"pid":"e25436ebdf88ba3a5678659e70a38eccf97ef9b1","tid":2350860,"uid":37375,"like":97,"dislike":2,"score":95,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"住係倫敦<br />\n勸大家租住先再慢慢睇樓"},{"pid":"7ba472b1016bb981ce6f503e1805729d91ac1f26","tid":2350860,"uid":275225,"like":35,"dislike":9,"score":26,"quote":{"pid":"d8a3309d8d1c473e67e8a82ff54428f5719579b3","tid":2350860,"uid":79563,"like":37,"dislike":9,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"LOCKDOWN 緊<br />\n<br />\nQ1 移條毛?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-02T16:32:39.000Z","msg":"Lockdown還Lockdown<br />\n移民還移民<br />